iommu/io-pgtable-arm-v7s: Quad lvl1 pgtable for MediaTek

The standard input iova bits is 32. MediaTek quad the lvl1 pagetable
(4 * lvl1). No change for lvl2 pagetable. Then the iova bits can reach
34bit.

